Package org.apache.calcite.rel

Class RelShuttleImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.calcite.rel.RelShuttleImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RelShuttle
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ProjectCorrelateTransposeRule.RelNodesExprsHandler, RelDecorrelator.CorelMapBuilder, RelHomogeneousShuttle
    public class RelShuttleImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements RelShuttle
    Basic implementation of RelShuttle that calls RelNode.accept(RelShuttle) on each child, and RelNode.copy(org.apache.calcite.plan.RelTraitSet, java.util.List) if any children change.
